25/03/2007 - 19:57
* Follow debuging memory deallocation once turbulence is stoped. You must
  ensure that turbulence_exit uses a static mutex to avoid several threads
  getting inside the termination function. For this, include now support
  inside vortex to handle static mutex, lock and unlocking them. See
  the source code provided by configure.in and glibconfig.h.win32 at
  the glib source code.
